 Require each party, prior to any hearing, to provide all other
parties and the examiner with a copy of any exhibit that the party
intends to introduce into evidence;

 Require each party, prior to any deposition, to provide all other
parties and the examiner with a copy of any document that the party
intends to use to examine a deponent;

 The manner of the deposition (telephone, audio-visual
telecommunication, or personal attendance of those who are to
